<xsl:include href="model://2b38c7eb-714f-4ae9-8280-ce7a4c99d93f"/>
<xsl:template match="ROOT"> <xsl:apply-templates select="ProjectBudget/ProjectBudgetLine"/> </xsl:template>
<xsl:template match="ProjectBudgetLine"> <xsl:copy> <xsl:copy-of select = "@*"/>
<xsl:choose> <xsl:when test="string(@refProductId) and string(../@refProjectId)"> <xsl:variable name="businessPartnerId" select="AS:LookupValue('bb34d696-6045-4bf9-89d7-7a4d34b239f1', ../@refProjectId)"/> <xsl:variable name="salesPriceListId"> <xsl:call-template name="getPriceListId"> <xsl:with-param name="directionId" select="AS:GetConstant('DocumentDirection_Sales')"/> <xsl:with-param name="businessPartnerId" select="$businessPartnerId"/> </xsl:call-template> </xsl:variable> <xsl:variable name="specialOffersIgnored" select="AS:LookupValue('895fba93-ea02-4f03-b629-7c54e5b45b15', $businessPartnerId)"/> <!-- purchase price list --> <xsl:variable name="purchasePriceListId"> <xsl:choose> <xsl:when test="string(@refSupplierBusinessPartnerId)"> <!-- by supplier --> <xsl:call-template name="getPriceListId"> <xsl:with-param name="directionId" select="AS:GetConstant('DocumentDirection_Purchase')"/> <xsl:with-param name="businessPartnerId" select="@refSupplierBusinessPartnerId"/> </xsl:call-template> </xsl:when> <xsl:otherwise> <!-- default purchase price --> <xsl:value-of select="AS:GetConstant('DefaultPriceList_Purchase')"/> </xsl:otherwise> </xsl:choose> </xsl:variable>
<xsl:variable name="salesTaxProfileId"> <xsl:choose> <xsl:when test="string(@refSalesTaxProfileId)"> <xsl:value-of select="@refSalesTaxProfileId"/> </xsl:when> <xsl:when test="string($businessPartnerId)"> <xsl:value-of select="AS:LookupValue('14ee4aa3-9d01-4381-a851-edf1d2a1c615', $businessPartnerId)"/> </xsl:when> </xsl:choose> </xsl:variable>
<xsl:variable name="purchaseTaxProfileId"> <xsl:choose> <xsl:when test="string(@refPurchaseTaxProfileId)"> <xsl:value-of select="@refPurchaseTaxProfileId"/> </xsl:when> <xsl:when test="string(@refSupplierBusinessPartnerId)"> <xsl:value-of select="AS:LookupValue('14ee4aa3-9d01-4381-a851-edf1d2a1c615', @refSupplierBusinessPartnerId)"/> </xsl:when> </xsl:choose> </xsl:variable>
<xsl:variable name="paymentAccountTypeId" select="AS:GetConstant('PaymentAccountType_Bank')"/> <xsl:variable name="date"><xsl:value-of select="AS:isnull(substring-before(../@DateValidFrom, 'T'), '1900-01-01')"/></xsl:variable>
<!-- sales price --> <xsl:call-template name="getPrices"> <xsl:with-param name="productId" select="@refProductId"/> <xsl:with-param name="priceListId" select="$salesPriceListId"/> <xsl:with-param name="ignoreSpecialOffers" select="$specialOffersIgnored"/> <xsl:with-param name="currencyId" select="../@refSalesCurrencyId"/> <xsl:with-param name="siteId" select="../@refSalesSiteId"/> <xsl:with-param name="date" select="$date"/> <xsl:with-param name="paymentAccountTypeId" select="$paymentAccountTypeId"/> <xsl:with-param name="taxProfileId" select="$salesTaxProfileId"/> <xsl:with-param name="quantity" select="@Quantity"/>
<xsl:with-param name="currentPrice" select="@SalesPriceEntry"/> <xsl:with-param name="priceAttributeName" select="'SalesPriceEntry'"/> <xsl:with-param name="listPriceAttributeName" select="'SalesListPriceEntry'"/> <xsl:with-param name="taxIdAttributeName" select="'refSalesTaxId'"/> <xsl:with-param name="isFromPriceListAttributeName" select="'IsSalesFromPriceList'"/> </xsl:call-template>
<!-- purchase price --> <xsl:call-template name="getPrices"> <xsl:with-param name="productId" select="@refProductId"/> <xsl:with-param name="priceListId" select="$purchasePriceListId"/> <xsl:with-param name="ignoreSpecialOffers" select="'true'"/> <xsl:with-param name="currencyId" select="@refPurchaseCurrencyId"/> <xsl:with-param name="siteId" select="@refPurchaseSiteId"/> <xsl:with-param name="date" select="$date"/> <xsl:with-param name="paymentAccountTypeId" select="$paymentAccountTypeId"/> <xsl:with-param name="taxProfileId" select="$purchaseTaxProfileId"/> <xsl:with-param name="quantity" select="@Quantity"/>
<xsl:with-param name="currentPrice" select="@PurchasePriceEntry"/> <xsl:with-param name="priceAttributeName" select="'PurchasePriceEntry'"/> <xsl:with-param name="listPriceAttributeName" select="'PurchaseListPriceEntry'"/> <xsl:with-param name="taxIdAttributeName" select="'refPurchaseTaxId'"/> <xsl:with-param name="isFromPriceListAttributeName" select="'IsPurchaseFromPriceList'"/> </xsl:call-template> <xsl:attribute name="refPurchasePriceListId"><xsl:value-of select="$purchasePriceListId"/></xsl:attribute> <xsl:attribute name="refSalesPriceListId"><xsl:value-of select="$salesPriceListId"/></xsl:attribute> </xsl:when> <!-- string(product) !--> <xsl:otherwise> <xsl:attribute name="IsSalesFromPriceList">false</xsl:attribute> <xsl:attribute name="IsPurchaseFromPriceList">false</xsl:attribute> </xsl:otherwise> </xsl:choose> <xsl:copy-of select = "*"/> </xsl:copy> </xsl:template> </xsl:stylesheet>

<xsl:template match="ROOT"> <ROOT> <xsl:apply-templates select="ProjectBudget/ProjectBudgetLine"/> </ROOT> </xsl:template>
